            </li>
            <li>
                <a
                    href="https://ink.library.smu.edu.sg/context/soss_research/article/4716/viewcontent/Choy___Li__2021_Factors_that_Promote_or_Predict_Infidelity_av.pdf"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                    Factors That Promote or Predict Infidelity – SMU Research
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a
                    href="https://primenjena.psihologija.ff.uns.ac.rs/index.php/pp/article/download/2345/2201/5195"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                    Personality Traits, Alternatives, and Infidelity – Applied
                    Psychology Journal
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

